00:20:56.519 --> 00:21:00.582
So Yahowah, Almighty, 'Elohiym, who is God,

00:21:01.905 --> 00:21:02.866
planted, established,

00:21:02.906 --> 00:21:05.988
firmly embedding a home to celebrate life.

00:21:06.067 --> 00:21:09.230
