00:21:12.991 --> 00:21:17.273
This environment was conducive to life, conducive to growth.

00:21:17.794 --> 00:21:19.375
It was a place to celebrate life and to embed a home,

00:21:19.494 --> 00:21:23.497
to establish and plant that which would grow, a dwelling place.

